    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB design-screening context described in the Claim and Requirement.",
